    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，美联储应降低费率以帮助关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-20/trump-says-fed-should-cut-rates-to-help-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统表示，随着美国关税开始过渡到经济，美联储应降低利率。特朗普敦促美联储在关于真理社会的帖子中“做正确的事”。凯文·惠特拉（Kevin Whitelaw）在彭博电视台上报告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-20/trump-says-fed-should-cut-rates-to-help-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 10:00:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Commerzbank首席执行官旗帜强劲的起点，一年一度的关税警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/commerzbank-ceo-flags-strong-start-to-year-cautions-on-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Commerzbank AG首席执行官Bettina Orlopp表示，今年的贷方开始了强劲的开端，即使经济学家警告说，关税的威胁将对今年德国的经济增长权重。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/commerzbank-ceo-flags-strong-start-to-year-cautions-on-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 10:00:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>港口港口使中国感到不安，CK和记旗帜会旗帜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/li-ka-shing-s-ck-hutchison-profit-misses-amid-port-deal-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[CK Hutchison Holdings Ltd.警告说，由于地缘政治和贸易紧张局势，全球商业环境恶化，因为香港企业集团报告的利润较弱，而港口销售计划在激怒北京后面临不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/li-ka-shing-s-ck-hutchison-profit-misses-amid-port-deal-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 08:44:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
