      <title>拉加德说，不确定性意味着欧洲央行无法承诺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/lagarde-says-rising-uncertainty-means-ecb-can-t-commit-on-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据克里斯汀·拉加德（Christine Lagarde）总统称，欧洲中央银行由于对贸易的不可预测性的提高而无法对利率作出坚定的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/lagarde-says-rising-uncertainty-means-ecb-can-t-commit-on-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 08:21:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
